        public CInteger getValue()
                  throws java.text.ParseException

      • pasteText

        public void pasteText​(java.lang.String text)
        Pastes text into the editor, setting the value based on its contents. A numeric value is interpreted as such, while other strings are treated as potential names of SharedIntegers which should be referenced by the value.
